    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>(This Jutsu cannot score a critical hit).</strong></em></p><p>Drawing your weapon, you become a blur of circular motion, sending a devastating amount of lead or iron in all directions with inhuman speed and precision.</p><p>Make three ranged Taijutsu attacks, comparing the result against the AC of all creatures of your choice within 30 feet of you. On a hit, you deal your [Weapon Damage] + 2d6, and the target gains 1 rank of the <strong>Bleeding</strong> condition.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d6.</p>",
